{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0c84d2c275","title":"致刘少奇电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ad57dc9b8b","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":2,"articleId":"0c84d2c275"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e48c8c04e9","type":"paragraph","text":"致刘少奇电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"0c84d2c275"},{"id":"aa8db42d51","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月2日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"0c84d2c275"},{"id":"96840cead0","type":"paragraph","text":"急须同晋绥当局成立友好关系，以便利红军行动。速从民族解放同盟或其他关系与晋阁、绥傅接治，其条件为：（一）晋绥容许红军参加抗日战线，划定一定防地，帮助解决给养，弹药。（二）红军愿意服从图氏之统一指挥，并不干涉普绥行政。（三）红军派出代表驻在普阁、绥傅处，以资联络。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"0c84d2c275"},{"id":"f3fca143bb","type":"paragraph","text":"11这是毛泽东致刘少奇电的主要内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"0c84d2c275"}],"page":{"id":"ae84a40fee","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"0c84d2c275","start":143,"end":143}}}},"__N_SSG":true}